short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This app is now disabled, but it used to track and share page visits and bookmarks for research and educational purposes.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension has been disabled, but an earlier version would collect your anonymous history and bookmark data to help teachers find new and useful resources. For more information, please visit the Doceo Center website at http://doceocenter.org.
